#WorldMentalHeathDay - You mean everything to somebody. Your existence is their resilience. Don't  lose sight of your own importance, do what makes you happy. We're only here once. Make yours about you & those that matter. The rest doesn't. If you're not happy then make a change

#WorldMentalHeathDay - There'll be those who try to thrive on alienation but it's their insecurity they promote to attempt to damage yours. It's your world, it's your life. Remember what's important and stick with that. Ignore those who try to bring you down. They're not worth it
